def shifted(im):

    r,c = im.shape

    x = random.randint(-r//4, r//4)

    y = random.randint(-c//4, c//4)

    img = np.zeros((2*r,2*c), dtype="uint8")

    xoff = r//2 + x

    yoff = c//2 + y

    img[xoff:(xoff+r), yoff:(yoff+c)] = im

    img = img[r//2:(r//2+r),c//2:(c//2+c)]

    return img
